item.title: Compile Error....?
item.dc:creator: @lolwut44 lolwut44
item.description:
@lolwut44 wrote:

Doesn’t matter, when the compile batch file is run, the first command executed is taskkill /F /IM java.exe which means to kill java.exe so it can compile without it being in use. It’s fine, just ignore it.
